in-bottom:0pt;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;If we decide to change our privacy policy, we will post those changes on this page, and/or update the Privacy Policy modification date below.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.15;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;This policy was last modified on Nov 20, 2013&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.15;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;If there are any questions regarding this privacy policy you may contact us using the information below.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.15;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: none;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial; color: rgb(17, 85, 204); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: underline; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;www.elance-clone.com/contactus&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial; 