(40, 'Create a profile', '&lt;p&gt;\r\n	&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:12px;&quot;&gt;Tell us about your professional skills, work experience, any work you have done in past for clients which can be added in your portfolio.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n	&lt;br /&gt;\r\n	Clients use all this information to find your profile in our system and invite you to submit proposals on projects.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'Y', 'Create a profile', 'Create a profile', 'Create a profile'),
(41, 'Win a project', '&lt;p class=&quot;normal&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:12px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height: 115%;&quot;&gt;Under Active Projects page browse different projects submitted by clients. Just pick the right projects which fits your skills and submit a proposal.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14.0pt;\r\nline-height:115%&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;normal&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:12px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height: 115%;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;normal&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:12px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height: 115%;&quot;&gt;The client may look at your profile or ask you questions about your skills. If everything goes right then clients will choose you to work on the project.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14.0pt;\r\nline-height:115%&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'Y', 'Win a project', 'Win a project', 'Win a project'),
(42, 'Work and get paid', '&lt;p class=&quot;normal&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:12px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height: 115%;&quot;&gt;Once the client selects your proposal, the client will transfer funds. At this point you may start to work on the project. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14.0pt;line-height:115%&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;normal&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:12px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height: 115%;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;normal&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:12px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height: 115%;&quot;&gt;You and the client will use a common area to exchange any communication or files concerning the project. Once you complete and submit the work, client will release the funds.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14.0pt;line-height:115%&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'Y', 'Work and get paid', 'Work and get paid', 'Work and get paid'),
