(1111, 'contents', 'contents', 22, '&lt;h3&gt;\r\n	&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:24px;&quot;&gt;Connecting best talent with best jobs&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:18px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Overview&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14px;&quot;&gt;We connect&amp;nbsp; employers and freelancers globally. Through our website, employers can hire freelancers to do work in areas such as software, writing, data entry and design right through to engineering and the sciences, sales and marketing, and accounting &amp;amp; legal services.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:18px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;For businesses&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14px;&quot;&gt;If you are looking to jump-start a project, broaden your reach or just simply get things done, you will find that elance-clone.com is faster and more cost-effective than job boards, staffing firms and traditional outsourcing. You name it and elance-clone.com will deliver results, often with a flourish: from writing code, crafting a marketing plan, designing your website, managing your day-to-day schedule and a thousand other projects.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14px;&quot;&gt;If you have skills and talent and are seeking independent work online, Elance-clone offers access to qualified clients, a virtual workplace and guaranteed pay for great work. To help make delivering great results easier for you, elance-clone.com offers a suite of tools to help make your work life as efficient as possible.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 26),
