(1196, 'contents', 'contents', 23, '&lt;h1 style=&quot;font-size:26px; font-weight:bold; color:#325a8c;&quot;&gt;\r\n	Get in touch with Elance-clone using multiple ways&lt;/h1&gt;\r\n&lt;h3&gt;\r\n	&amp;nbsp;&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;row-fluid row-borders prepend-top1&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;div class=&quot;span3&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;p&gt;\r\n			&lt;span style=&quot;color:#006699;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;If you want to report a problem, give an idea about new functionality or just to share your satisfaction with us, we recommend to visit our online community at soporte.elance-clone.com&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n		&lt;p&gt;\r\n			&lt;span style=&quot;color:#006699;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;Our employees and the Workana community will be glad to help you.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;/div&gt;\r\n	&lt;div class=&quot;span3&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;p&gt;\r\n			&lt;span style=&quot;color:#006699;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;You can also interact with us through our social profiles at Twitter, Facebook and Google+&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;/div&gt;\r\n	&lt;div class=&quot;span3&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;p&gt;\r\n			&lt;span style=&quot;color:#006699;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;If you want to read news about Workana, get any tips regarding working with remote teams or as a freelancer visit our blog: blog.workana.com&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;/div&gt;\r\n	&lt;div class=&quot;span3&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;p&gt;\r\n			&lt;span style=&quot;color:#006699;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;If you want to contact with us directly or in a private manner fullfil the following form:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 26),
